{"tid":328262,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係想拍返拖,唔想自己一個了","createTime":"2017-07-19T12:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T14:40:52.000Z","uid":59451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2d2551dc5e4162f860d26ca1819f514456d6f07","tid":328262,"uid":59451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:34:34.000Z","msg":"由喜歡單身覺得自由到依家已經覺得係缺乏愛情<br />\n無拖拍三年 <br />\n但係時候要搵返個人陪自己 買樓諗將來結婚等等<br />\n無奈現實生活好少去接觸女性<br />\n上網識我會比較容易燵著<br />\n<br />\n有冇人分享下?"},{"pid":"b1af2b31082bc2460626c17c22d259e704857274","tid":328262,"uid":53071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:35:47.000Z","msg":"睇下係自願單身定被迫單身架姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51559a6dc9180281f3a1f9b55a95d9969021efc7","tid":328262,"uid":59451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:39:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下係自願單身定被迫單身架姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n被迫單身都係自己選擇<br />\n睇你會唔會寧缺勿濫<br />\n玩又玩夠了 身邊十個十個都叫我正正經經搵返個<br />\n其實長遠黎講真係對成個發展健康好多"},{"pid":"ee4fe8107228ae1e1aaca539f63d9fc842614a23","tid":328262,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:40:45.000Z","msg":"想<br />\n不過寧願遲搵到都唔想再搵錯<br />\n所以冇刻意去搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2548c3212c84f13194101622e80424a334bf941","tid":328262,"uid":59451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想<br />\n不過寧願遲搵到都唔想再搵錯<br />\n所以冇刻意去搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隨時間過去 慢慢就會想,再急<br />\n女仔青春好重要 個個都鐘意18 22<br />\n不過我認同搵錯比唔搵更慘"},{"pid":"e76fdc182cc7c70607e04384f3f589b17f5cc96c","tid":328262,"uid":59451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:46:44.000Z","msg":"前排仲想玩下 依家僅有念頭都無埋,專心工作再搵對象"},{"pid":"5b6c8e1d5a009d1f722392516c899266b494755b","tid":328262,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:53:19.000Z","msg":"叫雞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61b7b63edd092ec359a0f1d0b27dc91939d93a9","tid":328262,"uid":59451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:58:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫雞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆街啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ae45eaf7d26697a3a64154563a38ab164dbb6c","tid":328262,"uid":59451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7bc1adbadc90dbccbf7e2127ee49d7ddf1ce0b6","tid":328262,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:12:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫雞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆街啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a6642b91802d89e3668dd14b3188f32d41bc47","tid":328262,"uid":59451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:16:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>叫雞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆街啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都話認真又叫人叫雞~~"},{"pid":"99a69fb2b2a537ee62d627e99605685fb8f1aeb6","tid":328262,"uid":59451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3a2883a12524cf8d7dd7cba9a8d5d29842946b","tid":328262,"uid":59451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T14:29:5